     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>Ad Authorem.</head>
   <l>TO make the <hi>English</hi> answer <hi>Latine</hi> phrase</l>
   <l>In Meeter meete shewes wit that's worthy Praise,</l>
   <l>But where the Subiects Godly; Lines exceede,</l>
   <l>All best Wits Apprehension there indeede,</l>
   <l>More be thy <hi>Piety,</hi> for such essayes,</l>
   <l>Prays'd then thy Wit to frame such Heavenly layes.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>I. P.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
